Detailed Description

This class provide Notification data.

The NotificationData class provides the data of notification.

The following example demonstrates how to use the NotificationData 

  //new NotificationData
  mND = new NotificationData();

gaia::core::PendingDemand* gaia::service::NotificationData::mpDeleteDemand

The DeleteDemand of the notification.

The intent to execute when the status entry is deleted by the user with the "Clear All Notifications" button. This probably shouldn't be launching an activity since several of those will be sent at the same time.
